  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Hold pre-implementation and consultation meetings with community members, the district, and traditional authorities to introduce the project to four communities in the Central Region (Elmina, Komenda, Moree and Ekon) and condition the correct attitudinal response so that the project is accepted by the target communities
Topics to be facilitated by resource persons during the capacity building trainings will include: Promoting Good

Hold capacity building trainings with identified women and youth groups in the target communities Dialogues/Town hall meetings will be held to follow-up on the capacity building trainings and will serve as a platform for a dialogue between the officials and citizens 
Facilitate the formation of a Women Advocacy Group in Local Governance made up of the beneficiaries of the capacity-building workshops as well as leadership of other existing women&#x2019;s groups in the four selected communities. 

Use drama and role-playing activities in community sensitization and education program and intends to form community based drama groups in the four targeted communities.. 
